name: Holder of Ethereum Stone Energy
description:
Vitalik, king of the Rock, holder of Ethereum (ETH) stone on earth. Vitalik believes that it is possible to create ETH from Gold, diamonds.
Vitalik chose Vuzu, today's pyramid area, as the place where ETH is generated because it concentrates the energy of the earth. This is an unbelievable dream. And, Vitalik was once successful. However, the formula is not yet complete. Every time Liza need energy for robot part, she has to have sex with Vitalik. It was definitely an exchange, Vitalik, the mighty king was truly captivated by her beauty. It is this episode that makes "God-built" Artwork so interesting.... In the story of the struggle, Liza's inner tear is very remarkable.
